snippet.title: Wayfinder: Early Access Launch Trailer | Gloom Break: Founder’s Season 1 Begins!
snippet.description:
Join Early Access Gloom Break: Founder’s Season 1 with any Founder’s Pack purchase!

►► Purchase a Founder’s Pack and play on PlayStation Today: https://store.playstation.com/en-us/concept/10002172 
►► Purchase a Founder’s Pack and play on Steam Today: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1171690/Wayfinder/

Early Access is here and the doors to the world of Wayfinder are open. Jump into the first Founder’s Season, Gloom Break. Enter the world of Evenor and prepare to take the fight to the Gloom!

Learn more about Founder’s Packs at PlayWayfinder.com.

#Wayfinder #GloomBreak
